{"word":"οὐρανομήκης","slug":"οὐρανομήκης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>οὐρανομήκης</b></el> <el>(οὐρᾰνο-μήκης, ες) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μῆκος'><el>μῆκος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>high as heaven, shooting up to heaven, exceeding high</i> or <i>tall</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>δένδρεα</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>λαμπάς</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>stupendous</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}